@startuml observation-memory-hierarchy
!include _standard-style.puml

top to bottom direction
title Observation Memory Hierarchy\n(host obs-api as single owner)

rectangle "Real-Time Capture (host)" {
  component "ETM\n(Enhanced Transcript Monitor)" as ETM <<infra>>
  component "ObservationApiClient\n(HTTP shim)" as OAC <<core>>
}

rectangle "Observations API Server\n(host, port 12436)\nSINGLE OWNER" <<api>> as OBSAPI {
  component "ObservationWriter" as OW <<core>>
  component "ObservationConsolidator" as OC <<core>>
  component "RetrievalService" as RS <<core>>
  component "ObservationExporter" as EXP <<core>>
}

rectangle "SQLite store" <<storage>> {
  database ".observations/observations.db\nobservations | digests | insights" as DB <<storage>>
}

rectangle "LLM Services" {
  component "LLM Proxy\n(port 12435)" as LLM <<agent>>
}

rectangle "Git-Tracked Export" <<storage>> {
  file ".data/observation-export/\nobservations.json | digests.json | insights.json" as EX
}

rectangle "Dashboard (container)" <<infra>> {
  component "/api/observations\n/api/digests\n/api/insights\n/api/consolidation/*\n/api/retrieve" as DASH_API <<api>>
  component "Dashboard UI\n(port 3032)" as UI <<api>>
}

' Real-time write flow
ETM SYNC_LINE OAC : per-exchange messages
OAC SYNC_LINE OW : POST\n/api/observations/messages
OW SYNC_LINE LLM : summarize()
OW DATA_LINE DB : writeObservation()\n(serialized lock)

' Consolidation
OC DATA_LINE DB : reads observations,\nwrites digests + insights
OC SYNC_LINE LLM : consolidateDay()\nsynthesizeInsights()

' Retrieval (in-process, runs alongside writer)
RS DATA_LINE DB : keyword search\n(FTS5)

' Export (debounced after writes, full after consolidation)
OW ASYNC_LINE EXP : debounced (10s)
OC ASYNC_LINE EXP : exportAll()
EXP DATA_LINE EX

' Dashboard forwarders → host
DASH_API SYNC_LINE OBSAPI : host.docker.internal:12436\n(thin HTTP forwarders)
UI --> DASH_API : fetch + poll

note right of OBSAPI
  **Single-owner pattern** (mirrors OKB).
  Container has no observations.db access:
  the .observations bind mount was removed.
  All reads, writes, retrieval, consolidation
  go through this one process.
end note

note right of OC
  **Triggers:**
  POST /api/consolidation/run (manual + dashboard)
  Dashboard AutoConsolidate: every 30 min
    when pendingPast >= 10
  Daemon (legacy): node scripts/consolidate-observations.js --daemon

  **Thresholds:**
  Digests: per day, skip today (auto)
  Insights: >= 5 unsynthesized digests
  Confidence decay: -0.05/week (floor 0.3)
end note

note bottom of DB
  **Dedup:** serialized write lock
  + stemmed keyword Jaccard/containment
  + LLM summary sanitization
  **WAL mode**, single in-process owner
end note

@enduml
